{"title":"canvas学习","date":"2019-07-18T06:33:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 18, 2019","L":"07/18/2019","MM-DD":"07-18"},"link":"Learning/973f37045c68","tags":["canvas"],"categories":["Learning"],"updated":"2023-11-14T12:07:06.466Z","content":"<p>canvas是HTML5新出的标记，是可以通过api绘制图形。使用之前必须的创建一块可用的canvas画布，之后的操作都是基于这画布上进行操作绘制。canvas是基于状态绘图的，先设定状态，通过方法执行。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>获取画布：</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> canvas = <span class=\"variable language_\">document</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">getElementById</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;canvas&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> context = canvas.<span class=\"title function_\">getContext</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;2d&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>可通过canvas.width和canvas.height设置画布宽高。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>其他方法</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">moveTo</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//将笔触移至指定点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">beginPath</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//起始一条路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">closePath</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//闭合至起始点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">lineTo</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//新建一个起点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">arc</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//绘制一条曲线</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">stroke</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//绘制已定义路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">fill</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//填充当前绘图</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">fillStyle <span class=\"comment\">//设置填充样式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">strokeStyle <span class=\"comment\">//设置笔触样式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">shadowColor <span class=\"comment\">//设置阴影颜色</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">shadowBlur <span class=\"comment\">//设置阴影模糊级别</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">clearRect</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//清除指定像素（动画去重影）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">fillText</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//设置文本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">font <span class=\"comment\">//设置文本字体属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">textAlign <span class=\"comment\">//设置文本对齐方式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">strokeText</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//绘制文本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">drawImage</span>() <span class=\"comment\">//绘制图象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"学习成果\">学习成果<a title=\"#学习成果\" href=\"#学习成果\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"../images/canvas.png\" alt=\"image\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"源码\">源码<a title=\"#源码\" href=\"#源码\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Chef5/canvas-Clock\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Chef5/canvas-Clock</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Vue学习-组件data和render","link":"Learning/8d0cb17b0653"},"next":{"title":"JavaScript-事件","link":"Learning/1444d05a63dc"},"plink":"https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/973f37045c68/","toc":[{"id":"学习成果","title":"学习成果","index":"1","children":[{"id":"源码","title":"源码","index":"1.1"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Chef Wu","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/973f37045c68/\" title=\"canvas学习\">https://blog.jschef.com/Learning/973f37045c68/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"July 18, 2019"}}